Package: ctlr
Type: Package
Title: ctlr: Shortcuts for data cleaning, analysis, and visualization
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Jay Cutler
Maintainer: Jay Cutler <jacobmcutler@outlook.com>
Description: This package utilizes functions from the {tidyverse} as well as {flextable}, {qualtRics}, and {boxr} to offer function "shortcuts" for simple data cleaning, wrangling similar types of survey data, visualizing data in tabular and graphical forms, and connecting and utilizing APIs.
